    <h2 id="dolphin-fuel-systems">Dolphin Fuel Oil Treatment Systems</h2>
    <p>
      Dolphin-designed and manufactured fuel oil systems process untreated fuel oil through a pre-filtration and pre-heating system to an <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">Alfa Laval three-phase disc stack centrifuge</a>. The heated oil has much lower viscosity conducive to easier centrifuge separation. The high centrifugal force within the separator bowl slings out the water and sludge from the oil. The centrifuge internally pumps the separated clean fuel oil to a local storage tank for engine or turbine use.
    </p>

